85
00:06:09,354 --> 00:06:11,117
You bought some hair too.

86
00:06:11,790 --> 00:06:13,588
With your money.

87
00:06:14,627 --> 00:06:16,857
So, what happened with the bar?

88
00:06:17,029 --> 00:06:18,792
You just had to be a rock star, huh?

89
00:06:18,964 --> 00:06:23,128
Shit, man. I want to listen to Larry King,
I go home and put the fucking TV on.

90
00:06:23,302 --> 00:06:25,770
That was a good location.

91
00:06:25,938 --> 00:06:28,771
Yeah, that's what my partner
kept telling me.

92
00:06:29,308 --> 00:06:30,741
Action's on you.

93
00:06:31,377 --> 00:06:33,140
